{"tid":1521862,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"和理非可唔可以唔好走⋯ 陪埋勇武一齊走啦","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:39:15.000Z","uid":112551,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"79d8d6f8dc04eb91f79589c9c4e9b70942813ef5","tid":1521862,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"PLZ"},{"pid":"0d97f977200fa68bdcf983b9bd711870e9af4283","tid":1521862,"uid":139282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span>"},{"pid":"e92a6364309882efab8df4ea8fbc867d4591b167","tid":1521862,"uid":273234,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"但係勇武留低就係想比和理非走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac9967f7f8f47bdb87f12f51083d69dfed24b7e","tid":1521862,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"會走就唔叫和理非啦"},{"pid":"a052ef75f490777c9e81056d35ff86e8ee07e403","tid":1521862,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ba8b9fb4560c27acfecef5a91a0e3d99e7a8b3f","tid":1521862,"uid":181088,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"點呀一時又屌佢地走<br />\n一時又屌佢地唔走前線走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2bd3e93e278020b586920e988a780b38d2c59e","tid":1521862,"uid":314979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJWu6ur.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJWu6ur.gif&h=4305a13b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70db4581bb2e2f2dc1cf353613f95c22f281ceb2","tid":1521862,"uid":274722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"唔分批走塞係狗鐵站等狗拉？"},{"pid":"509b8d3c373d7efce200eea55fc07eca14be2c91","tid":1521862,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3ba8b9fb4560c27acfecef5a91a0e3d99e7a8b3f","tid":1521862,"uid":181088,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"點呀一時又屌佢地走<br />\n一時又屌佢地唔走前線走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"和理走晒 啲狗仲猖狂，叫佢地低疏啲"},{"pid":"2bd728b1563642c124e361e092a05475999564d4","tid":1521862,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"冇走啊<br />\n永遠做你地後盾"},{"pid":"143379a5859